{"tid":924660,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲10日行程求意見","createTime":"2018-12-02T09:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T05:39:48.000Z","uid":110969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7f1eb6698f124621bef63f594507a11c83ad379a","tid":924660,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"9/12號朝   去到CAIRNS...去市中心報LOCAL TOUR +下午去釣魚+泥蟹<br />\n10/12 SKYDIVING / 出海潛水<br />\n11/12 SKYDIVING / 出海潛水 (呢兩日睇報TOUR 情況)<br />\n12/12 朝&gt; MELB/ SYD (先當MELB) 租車去彩虹屋&gt; PHILIP ISLAND<br />\n13/12 12門徒+ 直升機 之後再行下MELB 市中心<br />\n14/12 自駕去SYD (中途有咩地方好去下)<br />\n15/12 fish market &gt; blue mountain <br />\n16/12 hunter valley + syd 四圍走<br />\n17/12 BONDI BEACH + 市中心<br />\n18/12 未定下午機/晚上機 要睇機FULL 唔FULL (有咩好做)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8004a6653d6ca93ac47b0e254faf644eb4deeab2","tid":924660,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"Hunter valley 離Sydney 好遠架喎"},{"pid":"99ba23abea0c6886b9e293f3dba8f2feb8d8a86a","tid":924660,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8004a6653d6ca93ac47b0e254faf644eb4deeab2","tid":924660,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"Hunter valley 離Sydney 好遠架喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"都唔係話好遠既...<br />\n唔去HUNTER VALLEY 咁SYD/ MELB 仲有無邊度推介?"},{"pid":"28e3d16ce4ca6163e8addafa1e482cffd66c2c82","tid":924660,"uid":42509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:20:20.000Z","msg":"Mel去syd 可以去埋首都訓一晚（雖然冇乜野睇，但都叫去下首都）之後去Wollongong 南天寺蛋糕石8字湖。呢d一定去。<br />\n<br />\n反而mel既十二門徒石我就唔推介。city中心有條街噴漆噴得幾靚同埋city建築物靚過syd 。見意mel住city 租airbnb QV定QB係China town隔離好方便。<br />\n<br />\nSyd 南山又其實冇乜野做。叫做去過下。反而而家係摘cherry季節藍山渣多一個鐘orange附近好多摘cherry果園唔錯。"},{"pid":"08346c2621215a4392d5dd76ad49028d71dc87a9","tid":924660,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":