.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多地方都其實未點樣plan<br />\n暫時只係買左機票，內陸機同酒店/Airbnb乜都未攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbc0f19e07a9b0bb1a6a2fb3693f7a4c4c195a6","tid":924660,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1c7ac2044d27be244c0cdec2e8b176be39765ef","tid":924660,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"樓主我出年2月尾都去11日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫定行程如下<br />\n<br />\n26號朝早一落機就係墨爾本機場拎車先<br />\n跟住酒店check in<br />\n之後就去坐個咩蒸汽火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後可能四圍去下<br />\n<br />\n27號就去12門徒石，個到預玩一日了<br />\n<br />\n28號朝早返機場還車<br />\n之後坐內陸機去Tasmania<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係機場拎車先<br />\n之後就酒店放低野再出去玩<br />\n會一直由Hobart玩上去Launceston<br />\n中間去邊玩乜乜都未諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打算係到玩到6號朝早就由Launceston個場機飛返墨爾本<br />\n等到夜晚checkin返香港<br />\n<br />\n我未去過墨爾本，10幾年前就去過adelaide<br />\n<br />\n想問以上咁樣o唔ok?新手唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多地方都其實未點樣plan<br />\n暫時只係買左機票，內陸機同酒店/Airbnb乜都未攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:04:37.000Z","msg":"坐蒸汽火車有度麻煩就係自駕既話要坐返轉頭，而返轉頭班車要等好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06b4c03468be634eac143e4d19ea9816d343b59